    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is mitigated by the direct equivalency of the validation scenario to the COU and the conservative acceptance bounds applied. The assessment team notes that the experimental bench dataset (vintage 2025-11-20) and material property dataset (vintage 2025-09-05) predate the February 2026 model revision; re-validation against the updated model build is planned for Q2 2026 prior to final design lock.",
